  "body": "# Better Lanterns v1.3\n> Improves lanterns and chains models with an enhanced 3D look for a more immersive experience.  \n\n**Now Compatible with the new Copper Lanterns and Chains!**\n# 📝Features\nThis Resource Pack changes **Lanterns** and **Chains** by giving them a **3D model** and a refreshing look. Moreover, it changes the way the Lanterns are **held** in **third person**, to be nicer and a bit more realistic.  \n\n<img alt=\"How the lanterns looks in game\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/PGGrfcvL/images/23b2f53e3c5ad65d2f623fb6bc5aa5a3d4ff8f6c.png\">  \n<img alt=\"3D Copper Lanterns and Chains\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/PGGrfcvL/images/76ce324094359b660b97d531f1a0af976480807d.png\">\n<img alt=\"Player holding a lantern in third person\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/PGGrfcvL/images/ce02d0246bb34e5ccdd95db1f48662bfe088b5a8.png\">\n\n## 🌟Mod Support (Starting from Version 1.2 and above)\nThe following **mods** are supported (**Fabric** & **Forge**)\n<table><thead><tr><th><b align=\"center\">Mod</b></th><th><b align=\"center\">1.20.x</b></th><th><b align=\"center\">1.21.x</b></th></tr></thead>\n<tr><td align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/arcane-lanterns\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Arcane Lanterns</b></a></td><td align=\"center\">✅</td><td align=\"center\">✅</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/new-thin-air\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Thin Air</b></a></td><td align=\"center\">✅</td><td align=\"center\">✅</td></tr></tbody></table>  \n\n## 🔗External links\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/nico4play/projects\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/B6lsNn0.png\" width=\"40\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/nico4play/\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PTAiKsV.png\" width=\"40\" /></a>\n\n## Older Versions\n\n<details>\n<summary>v1.2 and older</summary>\n\n# Better Lanterns\n> Improves lanterns and chains models with an enhanced 3D look for a more immersive experience.\n# 📝Features\nThis Resource Pack changes **Lanterns** and **Chains** by giving them a **3D model** and a refreshing look. Moreover, it changes the way the Lanterns are **held** in **third person**, to be nicer and a bit more realistic.  \n\n<img alt=\"How the lanterns looks in game\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/PGGrfcvL/images/23b2f53e3c5ad65d2f623fb6bc5aa5a3d4ff8f6c.png\">  <img alt=\"Player holding a lantern in third person\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/PGGrfcvL/images/ce02d0246bb34e5ccdd95db1f48662bfe088b5a8.png\">\n\n## 🌟Mod Support (Starting from Version 1.2 and above)\nThe following **mods** are supported (**Fabric** & **Forge**)\n<table><thead><tr><th><b align=\"center\">Mod</b></th><th><b align=\"center\">1.20</b></th><th><b align=\"center\">1.21</b></th></tr></thead>\n<tr><td align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/arcane-lanterns\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Arcane Lanterns</b></a></td><td align=\"center\">✅</td><td align=\"center\">✅</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/new-thin-air\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Thin Air</b></a></td><td align=\"center\">✅</td><td align=\"center\">✅</td></tr></tbody></table>  \n\n## 🔗External links\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/nico4play/projects\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/B6lsNn0.png\" width=\"40\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/nico4play/\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PTAiKsV.png\" width=\"40\" /></a>\n\n</details>",
